        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Stop the broadcasts.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-07a5c944-7353-40bb-b454-6b09fdc8ef2c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-06-10/debates/81809c2b-d6b8-47aa-9207-33dea0b7eb6e/DefenceOfCrete#contribution-07a5c944-7353-40bb-b454-6b09fdc8ef2c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-97ed42d6-fdf4-429a-99a7-7532a3794ee5">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-97ed42d6-fdf4-429a-99a7-7532a3794ee5">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-97ed42d6-fdf4-429a-99a7-7532a3794ee5">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-97ed42d6-fdf4-429a-99a7-7532a3794ee5">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-97ed42d6-fdf4-429a-99a7-7532a3794ee5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-06-10/debates/81809c2b-d6b8-47aa-9207-33dea0b7eb6e/DefenceOfCrete#contribution-97ed42d6-fdf4-429a-99a7-7532a3794ee5">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I would have liked very much to have stopped them, and in some cases I have reduced them in number. I think it is a very risky thing to ask a professional officer, naval, military or air, to give a weekly expatiation on the war when, in the nature of things, although he may be very accomplished in his profession, he cannot know and ought not to know the facts as they are understood at the secret meetings.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-97ed42d6-fdf4-429a-99a7-7532a3794ee5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
