    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will the right hon. gentleman say something about the Air Arm co-operation?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e1283a9f-5c9f-4cfd-afc5-d5db29a565ca" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-06-10/debates/81809c2b-d6b8-47aa-9207-33dea0b7eb6e/DefenceOfCrete#contribution-e1283a9f-5c9f-4cfd-afc5-d5db29a565ca">
